      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for those who value function over form. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the roof and trunk, and a small dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few minor stains, but all essential electronics and climate controls are fully operational. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been regularly serviced, though it may require some minor suspension work in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that is priced to reflect its current cosmetic state.",
