    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 987.2-generation Cayman S is a purist's configuration, featuring the 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) for optimized thermal efficiency and throttle response. The mid-ship engine placement ensures a low polar moment of inertia, providing neutral handling characteristics through high-G corners. This example is equipped with a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle and a mechanical limited-slip differential, ensuring maximum traction during exit acceleration. The chassis remains composed with high-rate anti-roll bars and a rigid subframe, while the hydraulic steering rack offers unfiltered feedback. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive borescope inspection and a fresh fill of synthetic lubricant to protect the integrated dry-sump system. A mechanically robust driver\u2019s car for those who prioritize kinematic precision.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
