      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality, having been maintained with a high level of care. The exterior paint retains a brilliant luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and free of odors; the leather bolsters show only light creasing, and every button, dial, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has benefited from a recent full-synthetic oil change and brake inspection. The tires have plenty of life left, and the suspension remains tight and quiet over bumps. This is a turn-key vehicle, ready for a new owner who appreciates a car that looks great and drives even better.",
